{
  "stem": "10406.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And we were holding as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "The ladder was very tall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "There was, like, not such a strong setup, so he couldn't apply too much force.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "He would have fallen off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And so he saw it doesn't open.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "He went down and went away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Then we sort of stayed in that attic for a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We didn't know if there were other people there or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And then I heard-- when they took all the people out of that hiding place where I was, and there was my father's first cousin there, Kalman, who had the same name as my father.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And he was like an invalid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I think he got hit with polio or something or, you know, so his father supported him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They lived in an apartment there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was his wife-- he, his wife, and two children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were a lot of other people there, but they were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were taking him out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the little girl was asking, sort of in a crying voice-- people were crying --asking her mother in Yiddish, mother, mother, are they going to shoot us?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't remember exactly what the mother said to her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they took him away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that night, we decided to go down to one of the hiding places to look for food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother wouldn't let me go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, no, you stay here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm going to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then he went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I figured if he can go and find food, I can also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I, you know, I was in this other place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know where it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
